"7", "slug": "general", "subject": {"id": "100", "name": "General", "thumbnailUuid": "85c8f053-f68f-486f-a83b-79bd21080edc.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "186266", "pageViewsCount": 12, "slug": "whether-it-is-slack-teams-discord-how-has-your-team-used-bots-to-overcome-day-to-day-challenges", "createdAt": "2023-01-02T23:07:41-08:00", "path": "/p/general/whether-it-is-slack-teams-discord-how-has-your-team-used-bots-to-overcome-day-to-day-challenges", "title": "Whether it is Slack/Teams/Discord, how has your team used bots to overcome day-to-day challenges?", "descriptionPreview": "I know firsthand how annoying it can be to have to spend a lot of time looking up information or responding to the same questions repeatedly because I use Slack every day at work. I'm wondering if anyone else faces this problem as well and how you solve it today.", "featuredAt": "2023-01-03", "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "4752795", "name": "Hubert", "username": "hubert_chan1", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/4752795/ea334f32-df8f-471a-b32a-11867d5f5b57.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": false, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "515796", "name": "Ask Somi", "slug": "ask-somi", "logoUuid": "a19424ac-e188-4132-b174-b08afb9e3668.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 54, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 18, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "7", "slug": "general", "subject": {"id": "100", "name": "General", "thumbnailUuid": "85c8f053-f68f-486f-a83b-79bd21080edc.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "721998", "pageViewsCount": 43, "slug": "how-do-you-communicate-daily-when-your-whole-team-is-remote", "createdAt": "2025-07-10T09:45:27-07:00", "path": "/p/general/how-do-you-communicate-daily-when-your-whole-team-is-remote", "title": "How do you communicate daily when your whole team is remote?", "descriptionPreview": "<p>I can safely say that working remotely brings a special kind of challenge.</p><p></p><p>It sounds ideal until no one knows what the others are doing and progress feels... fuzzy.</p><p></p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "6558926", "name": "Aleksandar Blazhev", "username": "byalexai", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/6558926/ae02132f-a032-4ca2-ae67-485ca2018615.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": null, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 4, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 6, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "7", "slug": "general", "subject": {"id": "100", "name": "General", "thumbnailUuid": "85c8f053-f68f-486f-a83b-79bd21080edc.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "760990", "pageViewsCount": 79, "slug": "why-we-decided-to-build-cadence-2", "createdAt": "2025-10-09T04:09:35-07:00", "path": "/p/self-promotion/why-we-decided-to-build-cadence-2", "title": "Why We Decided to Build Cadence \ud83d\udca1", "descriptionPreview": "<p>Hey everyone,</p><p>Over the past year, I ve noticed how much time teams lose to meetings that don t really need to be meetings. The daily standup is a great idea in theory but in practice, it s often a 15-minute routine that interrupts everyone s focus, especially when you re working across time zones. My old manager used to tell us about his dating life in ur standups, which was pretty painful...</p><p></p><p>That s what inspired us to start working on Cadence a lightweight async tool where teams share quick video updates instead of jumping on another call.</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "8965006", "name": "Theo Crewe-Read", "username": "theo_crewe_read", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/8965006/4291bda9-48ee-4b7c-9df9-e5edd4f95e9e.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": false, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": null, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 4, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 6, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "356103", "slug": "self-promotion", "subject": {"id": "168", "name": "Self-Promotion", "thumbnailUuid": "de6414d8-ff23-41e1-a015-27b06a813efb.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}], "pageInfo": {"hasNextPage": true, "__typename": "PageInfo"}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadConnection"}, "relevantReviews": {"edges": [], "__typename": "ProductCategoryRelevantReviewConnection"}}}}